      • RENDERED

        public static final CommonRendererAsserts RENDERED
        Checks the attribute 'rendered', see UIComponent.isRendered(). Due to its nature this test must not work all the time correctly and should therefore considered as candidate for vetoing. The actual assert checks whether the given component is null or does not contain any children.
